Description
-----------

This determines the framerate to capture .
[TGA](TGA_%28file_format%29 "TGA (file format)") frames generated with
the [aviDemo](AviDemo_%28console_command%29 "AviDemo (console command)")
command.

Usage
-----

At the console type...

    com_aviDemoTics [int]

Parameters
----------

-   [int] - The framerate to capture at.
    -   1 = 15fps
    -   2 = 30fps
    -   3 = 45fps
    -   4 = 60fps

